          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card mb-3">
              <div class="card-header text-center">
                <i class="icon bi bi-bag-check-fill"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="card-title">Safe booking</h4>
                <p class="card-text">
                  Book homes online safely by our safety ensuring process
                  ensures tranparency within each transaction.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card mb-3">
              <div class="card-header text-center">
